in the Corporate segment in Equity in Earnings (Losses) of", "bbox": [143.8, 863.5, 1067.3, 884.4]}, {"text": "Affiliates.", "bbox": [143.8, 888.5, 227.7, 909.4]}, {"text": "16. Segments", "bbox": [143.8, 954.7, 259.6, 975.5]}, {"text": "Segment Information", "bbox": [164.6, 993.5, 349.5, 1014.3]}, {"text": "The Company operates three reportable segments: Consumer Domestic, Consumer International and", "bbox": [185.5, 1032.4, 1024.5, 1053.3]}, {"text": "Specialty Products Division. These segments are determined based on differences in the nature of products and", "bbox": [143.8, 1057.5, 1071.6, 1078.3]}, {"text": "organizational and ownership structures. The Company also has a Corporate segment.", "bbox": [143.8, 1082.5, 861.4, 1103.3]}, {"text": "Segment revenues are derived from the sale of the following products:", "bbox": [185.5, 1135.0, 773.4, 1155.8]}, {"text": "Segment", "bbox": [227.2, 1182.2, 288.3, 1198.8]}, {"text": "Products", "bbox": [650.3, 1182.2, 714.2, 1198.8]}, {"text": "Consumer Domestic", "bbox": [227.2, 1212.5, 398.0, 1233.3]}, {"text": "Household and personal care products", "bbox": [650.3, 1212.5, 968.9, 1233.3]}, {"text": "Consumer International", "bbox": [227.2, 1237.5, 424.7, 1258.3]}, {"text": "Primarily personal care products", "bbox": [650.3, 1237.5, 922.2, 1258.3]}, {"text": "SPD", "bbox": [227.2, 1262.5, 265.4, 1283.4]}, {"text": "Specialty chemical products", "bbox": [650.3, 1262.5, 885.7, 1283.4]}, {"text": "The Corporate segment income consists of equity in earnings (losses) of affiliates. As of December 31,", "bbox": [185.5, 1315.0, 1045.5, 1335.9]}, {"text": "2016, the Company held 50% ownership interests in each of Armand and ArmaKleen, respectively, and a", "bbox": [143.8, 1340.0, 1024.8, 1360.9]}, {"text": "one-third ownership interest in Natronx. The Company’s equity in earnings (losses) of Armand and ArmaKleen", "bbox": [143.8, 1365.0, 1076.5, 1385.9]}, {"text": "for the year ended December 31, 2016 and Armand, ArmaKleen and 